1. *Šok* je bio ogroman kada su otkrili da je predsednik korumpiran. (Shock was huge when they discovered that the president was corrupt.)
2. Kada su mi rekli tu vest, osetila sam *šok* u stomaku. (When they told me the news, I felt a *shock* in my stomach.)
3. Moramo se pripremiti za *šok* ako izgubimo ovu utakmicu. (We need to prepare for a *shock* if we lose this game.)
4. Nisam mogla da verujem da je cena tako visoka, to je bio pravi *šok*. (I couldn't believe the price was so high, it was a real *shock*.)
5. Prošla sam kroz veliki *šok* kada mi je umro otac. (I went through a great *shock* when my father died.)
6. Njen izgled je izazvao *šok* kod prisutnih na večeri. (Her appearance caused a *shock* among those present at the dinner.)
7. *Šokirana* sam njegovim ponašanjem na zabavi sinoć. (I'm *shocked* by his behavior at the party last night.)
8. Ona je bila *šokirana* kada je saznala da neće dobiti posao. (She was *shocked* when she found out she didn't get the job.)
9. Njegove reči su me *šokirale* i nisam znala kako da reagujem. (His words *shocked* me and I didn't know how to react.)
10. Upravo sam doživela veliki *šok*, moja kuća je uništena u požaru. (I just experienced a big *shock*, my house was destroyed in a fire.)